---
title: Kids' Easy Cheesy Quesadillas Serves 2 | with Guacamole and Salsa
description: More cheese please! These easy lunch quesadillas are stuffed with both Monterey Jack and cheddar for double the cheesy goodness. You also get double the dipping fun: guacamole and salsa!
